The Presidency in its statement, said Pa Reuben Fasoranti’s daughter was killed by armed robbers and not Fulani herdsmen as claimed by eyewitnesses. The statement by President Buhari’s Special Adviser on (Media & Publicity) Femi Adesina on Twitter reads: “President Muhammadu Buhari condoles with Afenifere leader, Pa Reuben Fasoranti, whose daughter, Mrs Funke Olakunrin was killed along Ondo-Ore road by those described as armed robbers by Ondo Police Command. “He prays God to give Pa Fasoranti fortitude to bear the loss.”